    "title": "Lead Investment Banker at India Ratings",
    "description": "India Ratings is actively seeking a talented and motivated Investment Banker to join our dynamic team in Faridabad. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout India Ratings:\nIndia Ratings is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in VBA\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Faridabad, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with India Ratings!",
